title: How to Deal with the Highs and Lows, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO234
itunes:title: How to Deal with the Highs and Lows, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO234
description: Any person's life, no matter if they are "successful" or not, is going to have ups and downs. If you're an entrepreneur, you can almost guarantee that you're going to go through a regular cycle of feeling good, like you're making progress, but then feeling like sh*t, like you & all your plans are falling apart & doomsday is coming. You need to know this is natural & normal...and the key is to learn a method of powering through these times & executing when your feelings are battling against you.
